                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d92">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-12-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 13, 1893</hi>
                        </date>. (Received December 14.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson reports that he has had an interview with the minister of foreign
                    affairs of the Federal Government, who declared on behalf of the same, that the
                    restoration of the Empire will be henceforth the object of the insurgents.</p>
            </div>
